short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Displays the 3D representation of an obj file in github

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: When opening a .obj 3D model file in git, rather than being presented with a wall of text describing vertices and facets, this extension allows users to visualize the 3D model with just a few clicks. Selecting the extension and clicking "DisplayNow" will open a small canvas in the pop-up of the 3D representation of the .obj file.
